@startuml
start
:User executes command;

'Since the beta syntax does not support placing the condition outside the
'diamond we place it as the true branch instead.

if () then ([not all ingredients' levels are already at zero])
    :Replace the ingredients that have non-zero ingredient's levels
    in IngredientBook by new ingredient objects that have
    the same ingredient names and zero ingredient's levels;
    : Show a success message and the updated ingredient list
     to the user;
else ([else])
    : Show a message to the user, stating that
     all ingredient levels are already at zero;
endif
stop
@enduml
